RENAME TOKEN bn_inv2pi TO M_1_2PI SINCE 7.24 # eliminated a number of libbn globals in favor of existing constants [7.24]
RENAME FORM "bn_inv4pi" TO "M_1_4PI)" SINCE 7.24 # eliminated a number of libbn globals in favor of existing constants [7.24]
RENAME FORM "bn_inv255" TO "(1.0 / 255.0)" SINCE 7.24 # eliminated a number of libbn globals in favor of existing constants [7.24]
RENAME TOKEN bn_degtorad TO DEG2RAD SINCE 7.24 # eliminated a number of libbn globals in favor of existing constants [7.24]
RENAME TOKEN bn_radtodeg TO RAD2DEG SINCE 7.24 # eliminated a number of libbn globals in favor of existing constants [7.24]
